  question: "H\u1ED3 Ch\xED Minh t\xECm th\u1EA5y con \u0111\u01B0\u1EDDng c\u1EE9u
    n\u01B0\u1EDBc qua t\xE1c ph\u1EA9m n\xE0o?"
